{"tid":684641,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"啲人係咪唔識落單之前諗好食乜","createTime":"2018-05-30T16:58:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T14:57:13.000Z","uid":87901,"like":40,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bc907ae0831ea94b5641424fed1fa1af0479c071","tid":684641,"uid":87901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:58:27.000Z","msg":"啱先去食飯 個場晚飯時間都幾full下<br />\n但得兩個樓面 幫人落單 執枱<br />\n咁我地睇好食乜啦 諗住叫 但比隔離枱搶先一步<br />\n<br />\n隔離枱: 唔該想要呢個餐<br />\n侍應：要啲咩嘅<br />\n之後佢地先好似發現個餐有野揀<br />\n但其實個餐牌係好明顯有得比你揀前菜主菜<br />\n隔離枱A:你想要邊個？<br />\n點知<br />\n隔離枱B：你鐘意啦 我無所謂<br />\n隔離枱A：你覺得邊個好食啲？<br />\n就不停係到推黎推去 搞左幾分鐘先落完張單<br />\n<br />\n完全目擊個侍應由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有乜幫到你<br />\n變到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來未揀掂 再變到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 揀好未呀<br />\n<br />\n有時真係唔好怪啲侍應黑面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜諗好食乜先叫落單真係咁難咩<br />\n點解要叫左先 再慢慢諗 得你一個客咩"},{"pid":"cf0be439a7d764ca525e675e7db482591b7bf694","tid":684641,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":46,"score":-46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T17:04:46.000Z","msg":"諗下都吾得牙？"},{"pid":"0167f420db97c713cd60533199e2e117d17a2c1c","tid":684641,"uid":37093,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T17:17:37.000Z","msg":"以前返part time做侍應 好多客都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔忙都仲話有時間等你諗 忙起上嚟其他等落單嘅客會諗你搞乜鳩落張單都落咁耐<br />\n有啲人好似唔識睇餐牌咁 下下都要人問 問佢佢又話要諗 到諗完 同枱第二條友又好似聾咗咁 要人問多次 然後佢又要諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4975ab522021db9e75297b88780294040b6aaa50","tid":684641,"uid":9286,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cf0be439a7d764ca525e675e7db482591b7bf694","tid":684641,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":46,"score":-46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T17:04:46.000Z","msg":"諗下都吾得牙？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T17:36:57.000Z","msg":"諗好先叫侍應埋黎唔得？<br />\n你假膠都唔該高質少少啦"},{"pid":"2b79c3e9f5494e7a6b92b48ce1ca82173ef940fe","tid":684641,"uid":76883,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"cf0be439a7d764ca525e675e7db482591b7bf694","tid":684641,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":46,"score":-46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T17:04:46.000Z","msg":"諗下都吾得牙？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T17:41:54.000Z","msg":"吾你老母<br />\n牙你老母"},{"pid":"dbc1e681c0a6906091380460307d84f32a458790","tid":684641,"uid":180035,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T17:45:12.000Z","msg":"反而係成日一坐低就埋黎問食乜 睇都未睇 之後企係度等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2db2b5c3f1d38a1da4a1bc27d9495dcc22de18","tid":684641,"uid":9286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbc1e681c0a6906091380460307d84f32a458790","tid":684641,"uid":180035,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T17:45:12.000Z","msg":"反而係成日一坐低就埋黎問食乜 睇都未睇 之後企係度等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T17:47:27.000Z","msg":"少客咪咁囉"},{"pid":"0be77567c0cd542a34f65801a7786c30219f54a0","tid":684641,"uid":87901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0167f420db97c713cd60533199e2e117d17a2c1c","tid":684641,"uid":37093,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T17:17:37.000Z","msg":"以前返part time做侍應 好多客都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔忙都仲話有時間等你諗 忙起上嚟其他等落單嘅客會諗你搞乜鳩落張單都落咁耐<br />\n有啲人好似唔識睇餐牌咁 下下都要人問 問佢佢又話要諗 到諗完 同枱第二條友又好似聾咗咁 要人問多次 然後佢又要諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T00:43:53.000Z","msg":"好似驚比人叫左野先自己會叫唔到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪都嗌左個侍應過黎先<br />\n見到啲侍應拎住成手野 啲人都係咁叫佢<br />\n過到去 屌 原來未諗掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"783abd5db39c8a2cdeba0179d0a977554a2ad4d1","tid":684641,"uid":87901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dbc1e681c0a690